mlab-node (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release: native Debian packaging of the M-Lab autonode stack.
    Replaces the Docker Compose deployment with hardened systemd services.
    Component binaries are built from the pinned upstream sources at build
    time; no Docker or container images are involved at build or run time.

 -- Measurement Lab <support@measurementlab.net>  Mon, 29 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
